OL,3,CBaby was not abused, teacher accused
OL,4,Cof murder told police
OL,6,FWARNING THIS ARTICLE CONTAINS
OL,7,FDISTRESSING CONTENT
OL,9,FA teacher being interrogated by police
OL,10,Fdetectives over the sudden death of
OL,11,Fhis adopted baby denied abuse or any
OL,12,Fsexual interest in the child, a court
OL,13,Fhas heard.
OL,15,FJamie Varley, 37, told officers "he
OL,16,Fhas not been abused" in the video
OL,17,Fshown to jurors at Preston Crown Court
OL,18,Fof the police interview after his
OL,19,Farrest following the death of 13-month-
OL,20,Fold Preston Davey.
OL,26,@wD@aOUxD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
