OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778223659
OL,3,CBaby was not abused, teacher accused
OL,4,Cof murder told police
OL,6,FIn the video, Varley is questioned
OL,7,Fover concerning injuries and videos
OL,8,Ftaken by him of the child.
OL,10,FThe defendant, at the time a high
OL,11,Fschool teacher, is accused of the
OL,12,Fmurder of the child, while his partner
OL,13,FJohn McGowan-Fazakerley, 32, is
OL,14,Faccused of allowing the death of the
OL,15,Fchild, with both accused of sexual
OL,16,Fabuse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778223659
OL,3,CBaby was not abused, teacher accused
OL,4,Cof murder told police
OL,6,FDuring the four months Preston was
OL,7,Funder their adoption at their home in
OL,8,FBlackpool, it is alleged he was
OL,9,Froutinely ill-treated, had indecent
OL,10,Fimages and videos taken of him, was
OL,11,Fsexually abused and physically
OL,12,Fassaulted.
OL,14,FVarley was questioned by police about
OL,15,Fthe multiple bruises or injuries on
OL,16,Fthe child's body, including to both
OL,17,Farms, his legs, back, throat and
OL,18,Fbottom and 24 bruises to his head,
OL,19,Fincluding behind his ear.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778223659
OL,3,CBaby was not abused, teacher accused
OL,4,Cof murder told police
OL,6,F"There's a lot of injuries here," the
OL,7,Fdetective tells Varley, "we are not
OL,8,Fsatisfied they are all accidental."
OL,10,FVarley replies: "I don't believe he
OL,11,Fhad that many bruises. He has not been
OL,12,Fabused. He hasn't."
OL,14,FHe is also asked about a Snapchat
OL,15,Fvideo taken around one hour and 45
OL,16,Fminutes before he and his co-accused
OL,17,Frushed Preston, who he had renamed
OL,18,FElijah, to Blackpool Victoria Hospital.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@aO]oD@YOUpD@cO]rD@QOUtD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778223659
OL,3,CBaby was not abused, teacher accused
OL,4,Cof murder told police
OL,6,FVarley claims he left the child
OL,7,Ftemporarily alone in the bath and
OL,8,Freturned to find him partially under
OL,9,Fthe water.The video was taken while
OL,10,FVarley was home alone with Preston,
OL,11,Fand in it the child is lying on a bed
OL,12,Fstruggling to breathe in what officers
OL,13,Fdescribed as a "distressing" video.
OL,15,FThe detective says: "There's some
OL,16,Fconcern about the content of the
OL,17,Fvideo. Why did you not do anything
OL,18,Fabout it?"
OL,26,@uD@POUuD@\O]wD@UOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
