PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778223659
OL,3,CBaby was not abused, teacher accused
OL,4,Cof murder told police
OL,6,FVarley said he could not recall taking
OL,7,Fthe video and thought the child was
OL,8,Fhaving a seizure as he had done before.
OL,10,F"He was fine in the bathtub," Varley
OL,11,Fadded."He's a long way from fine in
OL,12,Fthat video," the officer tells him,
OL,13,Fadding:J"In my view it's horrible."
OL,15,FVarley is also told an initial post-
OL,16,Fmortem investigation indicates the
OL,17,Fchild did not drown in the bath and no
OL,18,Fwater was found in his lungs.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@]O]sD@GOUtD@LO]uD@IOUuD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
