PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778223659
OL,3,CBaby was not abused, teacher accused
OL,4,Cof murder told police
OL,6,F"Can you explain how else he might
OL,7,Fhave died?" the detective asks. Varley
OL,8,Fsaid the child was "responsive" when
OL,9,Fhe pulled him from the bath but that
OL,10,FPreston was "not a well little boy".
OL,12,F"Was there any sexual motivation?" the
OL,13,Fdetective asked.
OL,15,FVarley replies: "Absolutely not. No."
OL,17,FThe detective tells him that when
OL,18,FPreston was adopted he was healthy
OL,19,Fwith no injuries but while living with
OL,20,Fthe defendants someone has caused the
OL,21,Fchild's death.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@KO]pD@TOUpD@_O]rD@MOUrD@cO]tD@
OL,26,AAOUtD@bO]wD@QOUwD@eO]
