PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778223659
OL,3,CBaby was not abused, teacher accused
OL,4,Cof murder told police
OL,6,F"We have not caused Elijah's death. We
OL,7,Fwould never do that," Varley said.
OL,9,FThe defendants had rushed the
OL,10,Funconscious child from their home,
OL,11,Fafter an alleged final sexual assault
OL,12,Fby Varley, to Blackpool hospital at
OL,13,Faround 6.20pm on July 27 2023.
OL,15,FMedics worked for nearly an hour to
OL,16,Fresuscitate the child until a decision
OL,17,Fwas made that further intervention was
OL,18,Ffutile.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
