OL,3,CBaby was not abused, teacher accused
OL,4,Cof murder told police
OL,6,FMcGowan-Fazakerley denies allowing the
OL,7,Fdeath of a child, three counts of
OL,8,Fchild cruelty and one count of the
OL,9,Fsexual assault of a child.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
